#Flutter Framework & Dart Programming Language
 It can be used on iPhone and Android.
 Pixel-perfect indoor map for the HUSS building that looks identical on all devices.
 It uses the Impeller rendering engine, which talks directly to the phone's GPU. This ensures smooth 60 FPS (frames per second) animations when the user is navigating.
 
 Platform: iOS & Android.
 Framework: Flutter.
 Language: Dart & C.
